//starting questions 
If user runs program
Ask “What time is your alarm?”
Ask “Standard or military time?”

If user picked military time
Loop every minute
Check time if equal to alarm set then ring

If user picked Standard time 
Loop every minute 
Check standard time if equal to alarm set then ring

//alarm rings
If alarm rings 
Ask “snooze” 
Ask “stop” 

//snooze button
If user picked snooze 
Create var time+5 minutes 

If time = snooze time 
Alarm ring 

//end button
If user picked stop 
End alarm 

